        <description>An area of deep water such as a lake, pond, river or fountain which may constitute a danger to the competitor or has forbidden access. The dark blue colour and the bordering black line indicates that the feature cannot or shall not be crossed. The minimum dimension is 1 mm².

&lt;span style="color:magenta"&gt;It is forbidden to cross an impassable body of water!
