Colour: brown 0 (white), 10%, 20% or 30% (urban) / 20%, 30%, 40%, 50% (non-urban) (min. 60 lines/cm), black; the colour and the line width shall be the same as for symbol unpaved footpath or track (506.1).</description>
        <combined_symbol parts="2">
          <part symbol="120"/>
          <part symbol="132"/>
        </combined_symbol>
      </symbol>
      
